name: pricks001
description: This one afternoon at work, in between carding people coming to the beer garden, I doodled caricatures of the people in the neighborhood. If you haven't met this guy yet, you've probably seen him on some "hipster douche" starter pack meme. Gladly, I never met this kinda guy, but I have been that person that said "not all IPAs are bad" and then recommend Ithaca's Flower Power. I'm more into hybrids myself, but I digress.
